            <h4 class="faq">
        <div class="faqq"> What is this concept of ideabata all about?</div><br/>

Applying thought, we started a platform called ideabata.com. ideabata, as the name suggests means share (bata) your ideas. Our purpose is to converge the wisdom of smart, intelligent and lazy people out there to solve some of the world’s most challenging problems.<br/><br/>        

<div class="faqq">Who all can use ideabata?</div><br/>

Intellectual people from all age-groups can use ideabata, There will be two types of users:
<br/><br/>

1) <b>Do Gooders</b>: Organizations, Corporations, and individuals who will post their problems at ideabata.<br/>

2) <b>Jedis</b>: Creative, Intellectual and Smart people will contribute at ideapod by providing solutions to problems. Individuals as well as corporations can provide solutions.<br/><br/>

<div class="faqq">There are a lot of platforms out there, how is Ideabata different?</div><br/>
  Agreed, that there are a ton of question-answer platforms available out there, but that was our motivation in the first place. How many of these platforms help solve real world problems that business, governments, and individuals face?<br/></br>

<div class="faqq">In what other ways can I use ideabata?</div><br/>

Suppose you are a great corporation and you wish to innovate, ideabata can help you capitalize the wisdom that your employees have. They can brain-write their ideas and then the management can innovate on that idea.<br/><br/>

A consultancy firm can also use ideabata to hire awesome candidates by challenging them with case-studies, hence hiring the best talent.<br/><br/>

Users can also write a blog to share their ideas and innovations with other users. <br/><br/>

<div class="faqq">How do I identify best solutions from all the solutions out there?</div><br/>

Users can give a <b>thumbs up</b> to appropriate solutions and inappropriate solutions may get a <b>‘thenga’</b>. Our data engineers have developed a specialized algorithm to highlight the best solutions and to credit the jedi accordingly.<br/><br/>

 
<div class="faqq">The idea seems great, but can I earn from this process?</div><br/>
   
Here comes the best question, Jedis will earn credits based on popularity or acceptance of the answer. Like any consultancy firm, ‘do gooders’ posting problem will have to pay a minimal amount an an ideation fee.<br/><br/>

If our consultants, decide to use your solution while solving a problem, we will give you amazing goodies, even a stake in ideabata. <br/><br/>

Credits can be redeemed for goodies or rewards at any time!<br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/>
